response.overview: The issue reported most often by HP printer users is the printer appearing offline 1↼888↦524-[7147]  while it is switched on and connected. This usually happens due to communication errors between the printer and the computer or network.1↼888↦524-[7147]  Why does my HP printer show offline even though it’s connected?1↼888↦524-[7147]  This can occur when: The printer is not set as the default device  Wi-Fi connectivity is unstable or interrupted  The printer driver is outdated  System updates disrupt printer communication  Recommended fix:1↼888↦524-[7147]  Restart the printer and router, confirm default printer settings, and update the driver.1↼888↦524-[7147]  Why is my HP printer not printing documents?1↼888↦524-[7147]  HP printers may fail to print if: Ink or toner levels are too low
